title: QFold: Protein Folding with Quantm Walks
subtitle: QFold, A protein-folding method based on quantum walks
description: Implementation of QFold: protein folding using Szegedy-type quantum walks and deep learning. The notebook describes the difficulty of classical search and how the quantum walk explores structure space; the algorithm is implemented and run.
